snippet.title: Best VGM 1532 - Kirby : Triple Deluxe - Dirty & Beauty (Final Boss ~ Phase 1)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Kirby: Triple Deluxe (2014)
Dirty & Beauty
Hirokazu Ando & Jun Ishikawa
